      <h1>Our Creche</h1>
      <p>Discover the caring environment of our creche program, where infants and toddlers are nurtured with love, safety, and early learning.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Safe & Nurturing Environment:</strong> Our creche spaces are designed to be warm, welcoming, and secure, ensuring every little one feels comforted and cared for.</li>
        <li><strong>Experienced Caregivers:</strong> Our staff are trained in infant and toddler development and provide gentle, personalized attention throughout the day.</li>
        <li><strong>Play-Based Growth:</strong> We believe in learning through sensory play, exploration, and nurturing routines that build trust and confidence.</li>
        <li><strong>Holistic Care:</strong> Activities are tailored to support physical comfort, social bonding, emotional regulation, and early cognitive development.</li>
      </ul>
      <img src="/images/people/our-admission.webp" alt="Creche Classroom" style="max-width: 100%; margin-top: 1em; border-radius: 8px;" loading="lazy">
