    <div id="Frequently-Asked-Questions" class="content-section">
      <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
      <p>Find answers to common questions about our creche program.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>What are the age requirements?</strong> Our creche program is designed for infants and toddlers aged 6 months to 2 years old.</li>
        <li><strong>What is the caregiver-to-child ratio?</strong> We maintain a low ratio of 1:6 to ensure gentle support and individual attention.</li>
        <li><strong>What safety measures are in place?</strong> Our creche is secure, with trained caregivers, childproofed spaces, and strict hygiene protocols.</li>
        <li><strong>How do you handle meals and allergies?</strong> We offer age-appropriate snacks and meals while accommodating dietary needs with careful communication.</li>
        <li><strong>Can parents visit the creche?</strong> Yes, we welcome parent visits and provide regular updates on each child’s daily routine.</li>
      </ul>
      <img src="/images/people/other-uniform.webp" alt="Creche FAQ" style="max-width: 100%; margin-top: 1em; border-radius: 8px;" loading="lazy">
